“亲妈”式打包物品，武汉高校暖心喊话学生。
"Mother" type packaging goods, Wuhan University warm heart yelling students.
澎湃新闻                      。
The news is roaring.
澎湃新闻。
The news is roaring.
有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻记者 邓雅菲 实习生 陈紫嘉武汉轻工大学工作人员在学生宿舍留下的便条。
Peng Pai reporter Deng Yafei intern Chen Zijia Wuhan Light Industrial University staff left a note in the student dormitory.
“你的宝贝书桌太大，已转移至隔壁1208暂存，不会遗失，请放心！”2月24日，一位武汉轻工大学的学生发微博表示，学校被征用作为储备隔离点，在整理打包他的宿舍物品时，留下了这样一张便条。
"Your baby desk is too big to be lost and will not be lost," a Wuhan Light Industrial University student tweeted on Feb. 24, leaving a note as he packed his dormitory belongings.
2月24日，微博话题“武汉轻工大学的宝贝书桌”引起网友讨论和点赞。
Feb. 24, the topic of Weibo "Wuhan light industrial university baby desk" caused netizens to discuss and praise.
当日，武汉轻工大学在其官方微信上发布文章《别担心！你们的宝贝都会乖乖地等你归来》。
On the same day, Wuhan Light Industrial University published the article "Don't worry! Your precious will wait for you to return obediently" in its official letter.
武汉轻工大学表示，学校各级领导干部、教师和辅导员亲自动手，对被征用的学生宿舍内现有物品进行仔细整理并妥善存放，且与学生现场连线，清点核对贵重物品。
Wuhan Light Industrial University (Wuhan Light Industrial University) said that leading cadres, teachers and tutors at all levels of the school had carefully arranged and stored the existing materials in the students' dormitory and connected them to the students' site to check the valuables.
武汉轻工大学宿舍整理前后对比图。
Wuhan Light Industrial University dormitory before and after collation comparative chart.
各高校“亲妈式”打包物品2月18日，武汉市新型肺炎防控指挥部床位保障组发布了“关于下达16所省属高校集中隔离点储备任务”的紧急通知。
"Mother-to-Child" Packing Objects February 18, Wuhan Municipal New Pneumonia Prevention and Control Command bed security team issued an urgent notice "issued by the 16 provincial colleges and universities concentrated isolated point reserve task.
澎湃新闻（www.thepaper.cn）梳理发现，上述通知发布后，各高校纷纷发布微博或公告致信师生与学生家长，表示学校将妥善打包学生物品，并做好消毒工作。
The roar news (www.thepper.cn) found that after the announcement, colleges and universities issued microblogs or bulletins to teachers, students, and parents, saying the school would pack and disinfect students' belongings properly.
武汉铁路职业技术学院的工作人员打包宿舍内学生物品。
Wuhan railway vocational and technical college staff packed dormitory student goods.
2月18日，武昌首义学院在其官方微博上发布文章《给同学、家长和老师们的一封信》，信中提到，学校将借鉴其他已被征用房间学校的好的经验和方法，精心组织教职工对被征用宿舍内学生的个人物品清理、打包和存放。
On February 18, Wuchang Shouyi College published an article "A letter to students, parents and teachers" on its official microblog. The letter mentioned that the school would draw on the good experience and methods of other requisitioned housing schools to carefully organize staff to clean, package and store the personal belongings of students in the expropriated dormitories.
2月19日，武汉铁路职业技术学院官方微博发帖称，“24小时，1000间寝室，老师们‘亲妈式’打包物品，宝贝每一位同学的宝贝，带走大家未带走的垃圾，请大家放心，相信老师，相信学校。
"24 hours, 1000 dormitory, teachers' mother-to-mother 'packaging, precious treasure of each classmate, take away the garbage everyone has not taken, please rest assured, trust teachers, trust the school," said the official Weibo post of Wuhan Railway Vocational and Technical Institute
”同日，武汉交通职业学院在其官方微信上发布文章《武汉交通职业学院致全体师生和学生家长的一封信》，信中提到，学校将专门组建由党员干部和学生工作人员组成的宿舍清理工作队伍，对隔离寝室内所有物品进行打包，所有打包袋将注明寝室号及床位，做到全程可追溯，确保物品不损坏不遗失。
On the same day, Wuhan Jiaotong Vocational College published an article in its official letter, "Letter from Wuhan Jiaotong Vocational College to all teachers and students and their parents." The letter mentioned that the school will organize a dormitory-cleaning team of Party cadres and student workers to pack all the articles in the dormitory.
2月20日，长江工程职业技术学院在其官方微信上发布《致长江工程职业技术学院全体学生的一封信》，信中称，“每一位同学的衣服、书本、铺盖、玩偶等所有物品，都会由我们老师整理、打包。
"Every student's clothes, books, bedding and dolls will be sorted out and packed by our teachers," the Yangtze River Engineering Vocational and Technical College wrote in an official letter to all students on February 20.
在整理打包的过程中，我们一定会像为自己即将远行的孩子整理行李一样，爱惜你们的物品。
As we pack our bags, we must cherish your belongings as we pack our children for our upcoming excursions.
”高校承诺彻底清洗消杀除了妥善打包学生物品，作为储备隔离点的高校还承诺师生彻底做好消毒工作。
Colleges and universities promise to thoroughly clean and eliminate all but the best-packed student items, and those that serve as staging grounds promise thorough disinfection of teachers and students.
2月18日，武汉科技大学在其官方微信发布文章《武汉科技大学致全校师生和学生家长的一封信》，信中称，学校承诺，始终把全体师生员工的生命安全和身体健康放在第一位。
Wuhan University of Science and Technology (Wuhan University of Science and Technology) (Wuhan University of Science and Technology) issued an article on February 18 in an official letter addressed to teachers, students and parents of students in Wuhan Science and Technology University.
如学生宿舍被正式征用，将细致做好同学个人财物的清理和集中封存保管工作，尽一切努力维护学生权益。
If the student hostel is officially requisitioned, the students' personal effects will be cleaned up and stored centrally, and every effort will be made to safeguard students' rights and interests.
无论最终是否投入使用，都将对有关场所进行全面、严格、彻底的清洗消杀，确保为广大师生提供安全卫生的学习生活环境。
Whether or not the final use of the site will be comprehensive, strict, thorough cleaning and elimination, to ensure that the vast number of teachers and students to provide a safe and hygienic learning and living environment.
2月20日，武汉工程大学在其官方微信发布通告称，学校会尽一切努力保障学生物品安全，贵重物品单独登记存放，确保学生物品安全隔离。
Wuhan Engineering University (Wuhan Engineering University) announced in an official letter on February 20 that the school would make every effort to ensure the safety of students' belongings, keep separate registers of valuables and ensure the safe separation of students' goods.
最终无论学校学生公寓是否被作为隔离点投入使用，学校都会对学生公寓进行完全的、彻底的清洗消毒，达到医疗卫生检测标准，保证学生公寓无安全隐患。
In the end, whether or not the school apartment is used as an isolation point, the school will carry out a complete and thorough cleaning and disinfection of the student apartment, meet the medical and health testing standards, and ensure that the student apartment is safe.
2月18日，武汉市新型肺炎防控指挥部床位保障组发布了“关于下达16所省属高校集中隔离点储备任务”的紧急通知，通知提到，为加大隔离点储备建设力度，经省指挥部与省教育厅协调决定，将武汉科技大学等16所省属高校作为储备隔离点交由武汉市指挥部统一调度使用。
On February 18, the bedspace security team of Wuhan Municipal New Pneumonia Prevention and Control Command issued an urgent notice, saying that in order to strengthen the reserve construction of 16 provincial colleges and universities, 16 provincial universities, including Wuhan University of Science and Technology, were handed over to Wuhan City Command for use as reserve quarantine points.
16所省属高校隔离点储备计划共计15000间，要求在2月20日前完成储备工作。
The 16 provincial colleges and universities reserve a total of 15,000 units, with a requirement to complete the reserve by 20 February.
隔离房间将按照一人一间一床的原则进行储备，高校储备隔离点(征用高校内体育场馆等建筑用于建设方舱医院除外)主要用于发热病人和密切接触者的隔离观察，原则上不用于轻症患者治疗。
Separate rooms will be kept in reserve on a one-person-a-bed basis, with the exception of university reserve isolation points (with the exception of the use of buildings such as gymnasiums for the construction of cabin hospitals), which are primarily used for quarantine observation of febrile patients and close contacts, and not in principle for light patients.
武汉市新增高校隔离点征用计划表。
Schedule of requisition plan for additional university isolation points in Wuhan.
床位保障组相关负责人接受采访时表示，“相关部门将根据防疫指挥部调度命令，视疫情实际情况需要，依法依规逐步实施储备计划。
"The relevant departments will, according to the order of the epidemic prevention command and the actual situation of the epidemic situation, gradually implement the reserve plan according to regulations," said the relevant director of the bedspace security team.
”6所省属高校隔离点分别为：湖北经济学院、武汉纺织大学外经贸学院(民办)、武汉铁路职业技术学院、长江工程职业技术学院、湖北工业大学、武昌首义学院(民办)、武汉科技大学、武汉工商学院(民办)、武汉职业技术学院、武汉交通职业学院、武汉纺织大学、江汉大学文理学院(民办)、武汉生物工程学院(民办)、武汉工程大学、湖北科技职业学院、武汉轻工大学。
The six provincial universities are: Hubei Institute of Economics, Wuhan Textile University Foreign Trade School (privately run), Wuhan Railway Vocational and Technical Institute, Changjiang River Engineering Vocational and Technical Institute, Hubei Technical University, Wuhan Technical University, Wuhan Jiaotong Vocational College, Wuhan Textile University, Wuhan University of Liberal Arts and Sciences (private-run), Wuhan Engineering University, Hubei Technical and Technical College and Wuhan Light Industrial University.
